title: Controlling Your Moods | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Controlling Your Moods | Joel Osteen
description:
If you want to reach your highest potential, you have to learn to manage your emotions. Your purpose is too great to let a temporary feeling keep you from your destiny. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
